Title: isfinite(timestamp)
Description: Returns true if the timestamp is finite, false otherwise.
EffectiveSQLsGenerated: SELECT isfinite(timestamp) FROM (SELECT TIMESTAMP '2023-01-01 00:00:00' AS timestamp);
EffectiveSQLs: SELECT isfinite(timestamp) FROM (SELECT TIMESTAMP '2023-01-01 00:00:00' AS timestamp);
